<?xml version="1.0"?>
<Fleet xmlns:xsd="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance">
  <Name>TF Willow</Name>
  <Version>3</Version>
  <TotalPoints>3000</TotalPoints>
  <FactionKey>Stock/Alliance</FactionKey>
  <Description>Difficulty: &lt;color=red&gt;HARD&lt;/color&gt;

Consisting of a skirmishing light cruiser, a sensor frigate, three torpedo corvettes, and two gun corvettes, TF Willow is designed to take and hold objectives. The Word Cadence can be positioned in the open to provide scouting, harass enemy craft and missiles with its Sarissa PDT, and launch cruise missiles at enemy spotters. The five corvettes can be distributed across space to capture objectives and strike targets of opportunity with close-range torpedoes and 120mm guns (be advised their anti-craft missiles require manually assigning targets with the Z key), while the Beyond Conventional defends your own objectives with its 250mm guns and anti-craft missiles. Beware, none of your ships can stand in a slugging match with the enemy's main battleline, so coordinate with your team and don't fight fair.
  </Description>
  <SortOverrideOrder>8</SortOverrideOrder>
